snippet.title: The Wind Waker Rewritten [TRAILER] A Zelda Romhack
snippet.description:
want to replay the wind waker with a new coat of paint?
looking for an excuse to play it for the first time?
like reading lots of dialogue?

https://www.romhacking.net/hacks/7002/
https://aproxm.carrd.co

instructions too confusing? click this. https://youtu.be/IaTCVYKj5Ks
don't want to go through the hassle of getting a clean iso all patched up? then you're in luck because slightly out of date versions filled with slightly more typos are available where other .isos of such nature can be found...

thanks for watching.
https://ko-fi.com/aproxm
